{"tid":520228,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[常備菜食譜] 用65分鐘煮8樣日本式家庭簡易小菜 可存放4-5日","createTime":"2018-01-05T08:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T10:48:07.000Z","uid":72478,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e334ddaf41b28e2af682f2d7e4ffc0641e376785","tid":520228,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:02:00.000Z","msg":"結衣BB套逃恥試過煮左一星期既午晚餐比星野源<br />\n而家日本家庭主婦好興係週末煮哂成個星期既菜/準備便當.<br />\n有D菜可以凍食, 有D菜就要微波爐叮返熱先食得.<br />\n<br />\n有人話成日食微波爐叮既野唔健康, 但成日出街食都好唔健康.<br />\n希望多D人可以留返係屋企自己煮飯食.<br />\n<br />\n日本呢個網好好, 好多唔同常備菜既食譜同資料參考.<br />\n<a href=\"https://cookien.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcookien.com%2F&d=5eF4tT49bOmdx1L6XUUpvwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=cb258ab0\" target=\"_blank\">https://cookien.com/</a><br />\n雖然有時有D醬汁/食材係香港唔常見/偏貴, 但大部份都係街市/日本超級市場(AEON/SOGO/一田)可以買得到.<br />\n<br />\n例如佢地網最新既食譜:<br />\n<img src=\"https://cookien.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/20171224_batchcooking_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcookien.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F20171224_batchcooking_b.jpg&h=f23e21a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有埋片睇:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0gKZ-JgSG7M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0gKZ-JgSG7M&d=5eF4tT49bOmdx1L6XUUpvwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=691ec565\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0gKZ-JgSG7M</a><br />\n<br />\n主食:<br />\n焗排骨/ 豬肉韮菜炒粉絲/芝麻醬豬肉片<br />\n<br />\n配菜:<br />\n拔絲蕃薯(日式甜蕃薯)/ 醃芹菜黃椒紅椒/芝麻油菠菜絲加紅蘿蔔絲<br />\n醃白蘿蔔/馬鈴薯雞肉<br />\n<br />\n材料(肉類):<br />\n排骨/五花肉片/豬肉片雞腿肉碎<br />\n<br />\n菜類/乾物:<br />\n菠菜/芹菜/紅黃椒蕃薯/馬鈴薯/韮菜/白同紅蘿蔔/荀/青豆/粉絲"},{"pid":"c1e46a2c364740cbe7e64150fc377ed295de4292","tid":520228,"uid":41311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T08:23:51.000Z","msg":"好健康 好夠菜又快<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186b95a10c148f34fc843828c97e6ddad7fbc6a5","tid":520228,"uid":140599,